gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 101, Magic 93
gameRecap.excerpt: The Warriors defeated the Magic, 101-93. Andrew Wiggins recorded 23 points and six rebounds for the Warriors, while Stephen Curry added 17 points, four rebounds and 10 assists in the victory. Cole Anthony led all scorers with 26 points (5-8 3PT FG), along with seven rebounds and four assists for the Magic in the losing effort. The Warriors have won back-to-back games as they improve to 38-34 on the season, while the Magic fall to 42-30.
